Step 1 — Create the WHOOP developer app.

Go to https://developer.whoop.com → sign in with your WHOOP account.
Click Create App (or "New App").
Fill in:
App name: anything (e.g. "My Dashboard")
Redirect URI: https://ytdashfinal.vercel.app/api/whoop-callback
Scopes: check read:recovery, read:sleep, read:workout, read:cycles, read:profile, read:body_measurement
Save.
On the next screen you'll see a Client ID and Client Secret. Copy both into a Notes file — you'll need them in step 2.
